We create a unique Internet marketing culture for our clients by raising creativity and strategy to the highest level on a foundation of accurate analytics. The hive works to reach your business goals faster and stay ahead of your competitors.

What we do.

 

Strategy.

The strategy answers how we are going to get from point A to point B to achieve the business goals. We digitize the project, estimate resources, time, framework, and pressure then turn this into a plan.

Traffic.

The biggest challenge for internet projects is to get a sufficient sample at the entrance to the funnel to test the hypotheses correctly and build up sales. We will provide the proper coverage in the channels your target audience uses.

Automation.

When a project starts generating stable, predictable results, for example, we invest a dollar and get two - it's time to think about automation. This process will free up time for other essential things. But first, profit!
